test.name: Prerequisite: the ALMCC shall configure the nodal AUMCC as not FGB ELT(DT) capable. Send a SIT 145 message to the ALMCC as coming from its own MEOLUT for an Australian coded ELT(DT), and DOA position in R.D. Congo. Expected result: the ALMCC sends a SIT145 to the SPMCC (and optionally sends a NOCR to 503 country code in MCC SIT format also to the SPMCC) because the SPMCC is FGB ELT(DT) capable.
